                  <div class="pt-4 pb-2">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center pb-0 fs-4">ID 찾기</h5>
                    <p class="text-center small">가입한 이메일을 찾기 위해 아래 정보를 입력해주세요.</p>
                  </div>

                  <form id="findIDForm" class="row g-3 needs-validation">
                    <div class="col-12">
                      <label for="userName" class="form-label">이름</label>
                      <input type="text" name="userName" class="form-control" id="userName" placeholder="이름을 입력해주세요." required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">이름을 입력해주세요.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                      <label for="userPhone" class="form-label">핸드폰 번호</label>
                      <input type="text" name="userPhone" class="form-control" id="userPhone" placeholder="'-'를 빼고 입력해주세요." required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">전화번호를 입력해주세요.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                      <label for="userStudentID" class="form-label">학번</label>
                      <input type="text" name="userStudentID" class="form-control" id="userStudentID" placeholder="가입하신 학번을 입력해주세요." required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">학번을 입력해주세요.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                      <label for="userDepartment" class="form-label">학과</label>
                      <input type="text" name="userDepartment" class="form-control" id="userDepartment" placeholder="학과를 입력해주세요." required>
                      <div class="invalid-feedback">학과를 입력해주세요.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                      <button class="btn btn-primary w-100" type="submit" id="findIDButton">ID 찾기</button>
